<p>Carbon is another Fintech company and one of the quick loan lenders that offer several financial services such as pay bills, invest for up to 16% interest returns, airtime recharge, transfer money, and most importantly apply for quick loans.&nbsp;</p>



<p><a href="https://getcarbon.co/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Carbon</a>&nbsp;was formerly known with the name “Paylater” but switched the name recently.</p>



<h3>Available loan types</h3>



<p>Carbon gives out both personal and business loans and depending on the information you give the platform, the system will calculate a specific loan offer for you. It takes only a few minutes for the loan decision to be made after application.</p>



<h3>Requirements</h3>



<p>Carbon promises not to bother their customers with too many strict requirements such as guarantor, collateral or document uploads, all you need to use the platform are:</p>



<ul><li>A mobile device.</li><li>To reside in Nigeria.&nbsp;</li><li>A valid bank account.</li><li>Your BVN to confirm your credibility and financial status.</li><li>A valid means of identification</li></ul>



<p><strong>Incentives:&nbsp;</strong></p>



<p>Carbon gives out bonuses and discount to customers who bring other customers on the platform using their unique referral link.</p>



